  <p>Sets the name of the desktop that the application is running in.
This is used by <link xref="Gio.AppInfo.should_show"/> and
<link xref="Gio.DesktopAppInfo.get_show_in"/> to evaluate the
`OnlyShowIn` and `NotShowIn`
desktop entry fields.</p>  <p>The
[Desktop Menu specification](http://standards.freedesktop.org/menu-spec/latest/)
recognizes the following:
- GNOME
- KDE
- ROX
- XFCE
- LXDE
- Unity
- Old</p>  <p>Should be called only once; subsequent calls are ignored.</p>

